_source.title: Login Failure
_source.issue: Users are unable to log in to the application.
_source.solution: Reset the server and check the authentication service.

_source.title: Account Lockout Issue
_source.issue: Users are getting locked out after multiple failed attempts.
_source.solution: Increase the number of allowed login attempts.

_source.title: File Upload Limit Exceeded
_source.issue: Users cannot upload files larger than 2MB.
_source.solution: Increase file upload size limit in server configuration.

_source.title: Browser Compatibility Issues
_source.issue: Website does not render properly in Firefox.
_source.solution: Test and update CSS for compatibility with Firefox.

_source.title: Password Reset Email Not Sending
_source.issue: Users do not receive password reset emails.
_source.solution: Check email service configuration and logs.

_source.title: Analytics Not Recording
_source.issue: Website analytics are not being recorded.
_source.solution: Verify tracking code implementation and configuration.

_source.title: SSL Certificate Expiration
_source.issue: SSL certificate for the website has expired.
_source.solution: Renew the SSL certificate immediately.

_source.title: Content Not Displaying
_source.issue: Some content is not appearing on the website.
_source.solution: Check CMS settings and content publishing status.

_source.title: API Rate Limiting Error
_source.issue: API requests are being blocked due to rate limits.
_source.solution: Adjust rate limits in API configuration.

_source.title: Data Migration Failure
_source.issue: Data migration to the new system is failing.
_source.solution: Review migration scripts and logs for errors.

_source.title: Email Notifications Not Sending
_source.issue: Users are not receiving email notifications.
_source.solution: Verify email server settings and SMTP configuration.

_source.title: 404 Error on Profile Page
_source.issue: Users receive a 404 error when trying to access their profile.
_source.solution: Check routing and ensure the profile page exists.

_source.title: Data Not Saving
_source.issue: Changes made by users are not being saved.
_source.solution: Check database connection and query execution.

_source.title: User Profile Update Failure
_source.issue: Users are unable to update their profile information.
_source.solution: Check validation rules and database connections.

_source.title: Mobile Responsiveness Issue
_source.issue: The website is not displaying properly on mobile devices.
_source.solution: Adjust CSS media queries and test on various devices.

_source.title: Slow Database Queries
_source.issue: Some queries are taking too long to execute.
_source.solution: Optimize the database indices and queries.

_source.title: Session Timeout Issue
_source.issue: User sessions are timing out too quickly.
_source.solution: Increase the session timeout duration in settings.

_source.title: Search Function Not Working
_source.issue: The search feature is returning no results.
_source.solution: Check the search algorithm and indexing process.

_source.title: Payment Gateway Failure
_source.issue: Users cannot complete transactions.
_source.solution: Check the payment gateway API status and logs.

_source.title: Page Load Timeout
_source.issue: The homepage takes too long to load.
_source.solution: Optimize images and check server response time.

_source.title: Incorrect User Data Displayed
_source.issue: Users see incorrect data displayed in their profiles.
_source.solution: Check data retrieval logic and user permissions.

_source.title: Data Synchronization Issues
_source.issue: Data is not synchronizing across devices.
_source.solution: Investigate synchronization logic and network issues.

_source.title: Payment Processing Errors
_source.issue: Users cannot complete payment transactions.
_source.solution: Check payment gateway integration and logs.

_source.title: User Feedback Form Not Submitting
_source.issue: Users cannot submit feedback forms.
_source.solution: Review form submission logic and error handling.

_source.title: Browser Compatibility Issues
_source.issue: Application is not working correctly on older browsers.
_source.solution: Implement polyfills and check compatibility.

_source.title: User Feedback Form Not Submitting
_source.issue: Feedback form submissions are failing.
_source.solution: Check form validation and server-side processing.

_source.title: Error 500 on API Requests
_source.issue: Users are receiving a 500 error on API calls.
_source.solution: Check server logs for errors and exceptions.

_source.title: Insufficient Permissions
_source.issue: Some users do not have sufficient permissions.
_source.solution: Review user roles and permissions settings.

_source.title: Incorrect Data Display
_source.issue: Users see incorrect data in reports.
_source.solution: Check data aggregation logic and calculations.

_source.title: Cache Not Clearing
_source.issue: Cached data is not updating as expected.
_source.solution: Review cache settings and purge cache manually.

_source.title: Video Playback Issues
_source.issue: Embedded videos do not play on the site.
_source.solution: Verify video player settings and compatibility.

_source.title: Browser Caching Issues
_source.issue: Old content is showing due to caching.
_source.solution: Instruct users to clear their browser cache.

_source.title: Analytics Dashboard Not Loading
_source.issue: Users cannot access the analytics dashboard.
_source.solution: Check database connectivity and server health.

_source.title: Security Vulnerability Detected
_source.issue: Potential security vulnerability found in the application.
_source.solution: Perform security audit and patch vulnerabilities.

_source.title: Form Validation Errors
_source.issue: Users are encountering validation errors on forms.
_source.solution: Review form validation rules and error handling.

_source.title: Cross-Site Scripting Vulnerability
_source.issue: XSS vulnerability detected in user input fields.
_source.solution: Sanitize all user inputs to prevent XSS attacks.

_source.title: User Permissions Not Saving
_source.issue: Changes to user permissions are not being saved.
_source.solution: Check database save logic for user permissions.

_source.title: Application Crash on Load
_source.issue: The application crashes upon loading.
_source.solution: Check server logs for errors and resource usage.

_source.title: Search Results Not Displaying
_source.issue: Search results are not showing for users.
_source.solution: Verify search index and data availability.

_source.title: Backup Process Failure
_source.issue: Automated backup process is failing.
_source.solution: Check backup scripts and storage availability.

_source.title: Localization Issues
_source.issue: Some text is not translated in the application.
_source.solution: Review localization files and translations.

_source.title: Chat Feature Not Working
_source.issue: The chat feature is not functioning for users.
_source.solution: Check WebSocket connection and server settings.

_source.title: Data Export Failure
_source.issue: Users cannot export data from the application.
_source.solution: Check export function and permissions.

_source.title: API Documentation Outdated
_source.issue: API documentation is not up-to-date.
_source.solution: Review and update API documentation.

_source.title: Content Delivery Network (CDN) Issues
_source.issue: CDN is not serving resources correctly.
_source.solution: Check CDN configuration and cache settings.

_source.title: Server Overload
_source.issue: Server is experiencing high load and slow response times.
_source.solution: Scale server resources and review load balancer settings.

_source.title: User Account Deactivation Issues
_source.issue: Users cannot deactivate their accounts.
_source.solution: Review account deactivation logic and permissions.

_source.title: Reporting Feature Not Functioning
_source.issue: The reporting feature is not generating reports.
_source.solution: Check reporting logic and data sources.

_source.title: Network Connectivity Issues
_source.issue: Users are experiencing intermittent network connectivity.
_source.solution: Check server network configuration and health.

_source.title: Session Storage Issues
_source.issue: User session data is not being stored properly.
_source.solution: Check session storage configuration.

_source.title: Data Import Errors
_source.issue: Users are encountering errors when importing data.
_source.solution: Review import function and error handling.

_source.title: Legacy Code Issues
_source.issue: Legacy code is causing compatibility issues.
_source.solution: Refactor legacy code and ensure compatibility.

_source.title: Security Audit Recommendations Not Implemented
_source.issue: Previous security audit recommendations have not been implemented.
_source.solution: Review and implement all outstanding recommendations.

_source.title: Unexpected Application Behavior
_source.issue: Users report unexpected behavior in the application.
_source.solution: Investigate user reports and server logs.

_source.title: Third-party Integration Failure
_source.issue: Integration with third-party service is failing.
_source.solution: Check API keys and service status.

_source.title: Unresponsive Design Elements
_source.issue: Certain design elements are unresponsive.
_source.solution: Review CSS and HTML for responsive design issues.

_source.title: Error Messages Not Displaying
_source.issue: Error messages are not visible to users.
_source.solution: Ensure error messages are displayed in the UI.

_source.title: Slow Loading Times
_source.issue: Pages are loading slowly for users.
_source.solution: Optimize images and reduce server response time.

_source.title: Multiple Login Attempts Detected
_source.issue: Multiple failed login attempts detected for an account.
_source.solution: Implement account lockout mechanism after failed attempts.

_source.title: Server Maintenance Notification
_source.issue: Users are not receiving notifications about server maintenance.
_source.solution: Check notification settings and delivery mechanisms.

_source.title: Inconsistent UI Behavior
_source.issue: UI behavior is inconsistent across different browsers.
_source.solution: Test UI across major browsers and resolve discrepancies.

_source.title: Demo
_source.issue: My PC not working due lack of memory.
_source.solution: Upgrade RAM
